title: NTR's Nannaku Prematho teaser to be released on October 21
text: Young Tiger NTR is busy shooting for his upcoming film Nannaku Prematho in Sukumar's direction. As per the latest update, the teaser of the film will be launched on October 21st at 6.30 PM as a Dusheera treat for the audience. The film unit has recently completed a long schedule in London and the next schedule will soon begin in Spain. The first look poster, which was released on the eve of Vinayaka Chavithi, has caught on big time with the audience. Rakul Preet is the female lead in the film which also features Jagapathi Babu and Rajendra Prasad in crucial roles. Devi Sri Prasad is the music composer for the film.
